    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's not just a break though. i mean i've taken breaks. i sit in this apartment and it's like the world just moves on around me and i'm stuck in a loop. everything feels so empty. if i actually just disappeared, like just... gone, i feel like the silence would just be the same as it is now. maybe even better.",
